snippet.textDisplay:
I don’t know more about music. but I listen to good music and always appreciate it. Very classy music that was.
I enjoyed the voices. Both singers are legends. But I believe if they give more singing to Madam Abida Parveen that will be nicer. Madam Naseebo sings on high notes and Madam Abida sings on high and low notes.
The song will be more melodious if Madam Abida starts this song and Madam Naseebo pitches in only for high notes.
It's just my opinion. 
Classy song Classy demonstration. The lyrics rock. Video shooting 100 per cent perfect
